Usage: ./my_world [option | map]
3D map editor

Option(s):
	-h                 Display usage

Interaction(s):
	Ctrl + o           load an existing map
	Ctrl + s           save the current map
	Ctrl + n           create a new map
	Ctrl + e           enlarge by one in the two dimensions the map
	Ctrl + r           reduce bu one in the two dimensions the map
	Ctrl + =           switch to null level mod
	Ctrl + u           switch to up level mod
	Ctrl + d           switch to down level mod
	Echap              quit the game
	Arrows             move around the map
	Page up            zoom +
	Page down          zoom -

N.B. : You can also use buttons displayed on the screen
